  • Classes

    Description
    GameStuff
    The GameStuff class encapsulates various functionalities for game management, such as score calculation, saving/loading game states, and restarting levels.
    GridClass
    The GridClass manages and renders a grid structure for a game level using JavaFX.
    HighScoreTable
    The HighScoreTable class manages the high scores for different levels in a game.
    PlayerInventory
    The PlayerInventory class represents a player's inventory in a game.
    PlayerProfile
    The PlayerProfile class represents a player's profile in the game.
    ProfileManager
    The `ProfileManager` class manages player profiles and provides methods to access and manipulate them.
